大多数遇难者都是前去祈福的[[香客|香客]]，[[泰国皇家警察|泰国皇家警察]]确认事件造成20人死，125人受伤<ref name="bbc victims">{{cite news|title=Bangkok bomb: Victims and survivors|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-33970145|accessdate=2015-08-19|date=2015-08-19|publisher=BBC News|department=Asia|archive-date=2015-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819000435/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-33970145|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。受伤者多来自马来西亚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/08/22/Loved-ones-bid-farewell-to-two-Bangkok-blast-victims/|title=Loved ones bid farewell to two Bangkok blast victims|work=thestar.com.my|accessdate=2015-08-31|archive-date=2015-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150823140152/http://www.thestar.com.my/News/Nation/2015/08/22/Loved-ones-bid-farewell-to-two-Bangkok-blast-victims/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、中華人民共和國<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education-community/article/1851344/they-did-their-best-father-hong-kong-student|title=Bodies of two women killed in Bangkok bombing flown home to Hong Kong|date=2015-08-21|work=[[南华早报|南华早报]]|accessdate=2015-08-31|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825205533/http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/education-community/article/1851344/they-did-their-best-father-hong-kong-student|dead-url=no}}</ref>、印度尼西亚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://en.metrotvnews.com/read/2015/08/18/159258/an-indonesian-killed-in-bangkok-blast|title=An Indonesian Killed in Bangkok Blast|author=metrotvnews developer|work=metrotvnews.com|access-date=2015-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005043943/http://en.metrotvnews.com/read/2015/08/18/159258/an-indonesian-killed-in-bangkok-blast|archive-date=2015-10-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和新加坡<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/bangkok-blast-singaporean/2067574.html|title=Bangkok blast: Singaporean who died lost her father less than a month ago|work=Channel NewsAsia|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825074543/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/singapore/bangkok-blast-singaporean/2067574.html|archivedate=2015-08-25|accessdate=2015-08-31}}</ref>。死者幾乎都是華裔人士。

==调查==
调查人员表示他们“确信”在现场留下背包的一名男子是爆炸案的嫌犯。根据已经在全世界播出的[[闭路电视|监控摄像头]]画面，该名男子身着短裤和黄色T恤衫，他坐在长凳上将深色背包脱下，然后站起身来把背包塞进凳子下方，走到一边掏出他的电话<ref name="BBC Sketch"/>。嫌犯很可能已从小巷乘坐[[嘟嘟车|三轮摩托车]]抵达华南蓬火车站附近<ref>{{Cite news | title = Tuk-Tuk Driver who took Bomber to Shrine comes forward | date = 2015-08-20 | publisher = Khaosod English | url = http://www.khaosodenglish.com/detail.php?newsid=1440073727&section=12&typecate=06 | accessdate = 2015-08-20 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085831/http://www.khaosodenglish.com/detail.php?newsid=1440073727&section=12&typecate=06 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

有些报章宣称四面佛炸弹袭击中的安全录像中拍到的男子被当局叫做穆罕默德·缪斯银（{{lang|en|Mohamad Museyin}}），调查员把排查重点锁定在沙吞路一带的一所廉价旅馆中，他们认为嫌犯就藏身此地<ref>{{Cite news|title = Bangkok Blast Mohamad Museyin Identified Prime Suspect Bombings By Thai Police|newspaper = [[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|url = http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/bangkok-blast-mohamad-museyin-identified-prime-suspect-bombings-by-thai-police-1516611|accessdate = 2015-08-23|archive-date = 2015-08-23|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150823141558/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/bangkok-blast-mohamad-museyin-identified-prime-suspect-bombings-by-thai-police-1516611|dead-url = no}}</ref>。然而这一消息很快被泰国当局驳回<ref>{{cite web|title=Govt warns netizens on blast posts|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/general/665024/govt-warns-netizens-on-blast-posts|website=Bangkok Post|accessdate=2015-08-31}}</ref>。

泰国警察局长表示，袭击事件是通过网络实施的，并出具了嫌犯的大致图像。警方还表示，出现在同一录像中的另外两个人也被当作嫌犯<ref name="BBC Sketch">{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-33984177 |title=Bangkok bomb: Erawan shrine attacker was 'part of network', police say |accessdate=2015-08-19 |date=2015-08-19 |department=Asia |publisher=BBC News |archive-date=2015-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150819073521/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-33984177 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

一名出租车司机后来证实嫌犯曾上过他的车，并形容他“不慌不忙，显得很平静，就像个普通的顾客，但不是泰国人。”司机还谈到一路上听到他说着自己不清楚的语言<ref>{{Cite news|title = Bangkok authorities clear pair seen before shrine bombing, say key suspect spoke foreign language|newspaper = [[日本时报|日本时报]]|url = http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/08/21/world/crime-legal-world/bangkok-authorities-clear-pair-seen-shrine-bombing-say-key-suspect-spoke-foreign-language/|accessdate = 2015-08-15|archive-date = 2015-10-08|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151008093207/http://www.japantimes.co.jp/news/2015/08/21/world/crime-legal-world/bangkok-authorities-clear-pair-seen-shrine-bombing-say-key-suspect-spoke-foreign-language/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2015年8月29日，警方逮捕了一名与爆炸案有关的28岁男子。他并不承认制造案件，但他涉嫌参与其中。该男子被认为是土耳其公民，在他的公寓里警方还发现了制造炸弹的组件和几本假护照<ref>{{Cite web|title = Bangkok bomb: Thai police arrest man over Erawan blast - BBC News|url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34095603|accessdate = 2015-08-29|archive-date = 2015-08-29|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150829183957/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-34095603|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Bangkok bomb suspect is 'Turkish national': Thai military - Khaleej Times|url = http://khaleejtimes.com/international/rest-of-asia/bangkok-bomb-suspect-is-turkish-national-thai-military|website = khaleejtimes.com|accessdate = 2015-08-29|archive-date = 2015-09-25|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925112336/http://khaleejtimes.com/international/rest-of-asia/bangkok-bomb-suspect-is-turkish-national-thai-military|dead-url = no}}</ref>。事后调查泰國警方在曼谷東部郊區逮捕的人是持有偽造土耳其護照的中國籍男子穆罕默德·比拉特克，並檢獲近200本偽造土耳其護照。

这起爆炸案怀疑是由[[泛突厥主义|泛突厥主义]]的[[新法西斯|新法西斯]]土耳其极端[[民族主义|民族主义]]组织[[灰狼|灰狼]]（kok bori），为了报复泰国在今年7月将[[维吾尔族|维吾尔族]]恐怖嫌犯驱逐回中国，而不让他们去土耳其避难而实施的。被警方逮捕的与爆炸案有关系的土耳其男子，名叫阿德姆·卡拉达格（{{lang|en|Adem Karadag}}）（就是穆罕默德·比拉特克）。灰狼被媒体形容为恐怖组织，该组织以暗杀并谋杀记者、自由主义者和土耳其左翼分子而知名，其成员[[莫梅特·阿里·阿加|莫梅特·阿里·阿加]]曾{{le|教皇约翰·保罗二世谋杀未遂案|Pope John Paul II assassination attempt|企图暗杀}}教皇[[约翰·保罗二世|约翰·保罗二世]]，参加过[[纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争|纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫战争]]和有穆斯林和突厥人参加的[[车臣战争|车臣战争]]。他们的目标是将所有的穆斯林突厥民族统一为一个横跨中亚至[[巴尔干半岛|巴尔干半岛]]的统一国家<ref>{{cite news |last=Sherwell   |first=Philip |date=2015-08-29 |title=Bangkok bombing: Was it the Grey Wolves of Turkey? |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/thailand/11832701/Bangkok-bombing-Was-it-the-Grey-Wolves-of-Turkey.html |newspaper=The Telegraph |accessdate=2015-08-31 |archive-date=2015-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150831195641/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/thailand/11832701/Bangkok-bombing-Was-it-the-Grey-Wolves-of-Turkey.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last= Murdoch  |first= Lindsay|date= 2015-08-30|title= Bangkok bombing: Who are the Turkish terrorist group the Grey Wolves?|url= http://www.smh.com.au/world/bangkok-bombing-who-are-the-turkish-terrorist-group-the-grey-wolves-20150830-gjavjz.html|newspaper= The Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate= 2015-08-31|archive-date= 2015-08-30|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150830033643/http://www.smh.com.au/world/bangkok-bombing-who-are-the-turkish-terrorist-group-the-grey-wolves-20150830-gjavjz.html|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Murdoch   |first=Lindsay |date=2015-08-30 |title=Grey Wolves Make Prime Suspects in Bangkok Bombing Arrest |url=http://phuketwan.com/tourism/grey-wolves-make-prime-suspects-bangkok-bombing-23081/ |newspaper=Phuket Wan   |accessdate=2015-08-31 |archive-date=2015-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150901023128/http://phuketwan.com/tourism/grey-wolves-make-prime-suspects-bangkok-bombing-23081/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news  |last= Rossin